description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nAbsorbs the enemy's MP when attacking with Magic skills, until it reaches 0.
description.name: MP Eater

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nMeditate for a bit to temporarily boost up the magic attack of party members around the area.\nRequired Skill : #cAt least Level 3 on MP Eater#
description.name: Meditation

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nUse the arrow keys to teleport to other places in the same map on a set distance.
description.name: Teleport

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nTemporarily slows down the movement of up to 6 monsters. Cannot be used on the same monsters more than twice in a row.\nRequired Skill : #cAt least Level 5 on Teleport#
description.name: Slow

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 30]\nAttacks a single monster with a sharp piece of Ice. The monster will freeze if hit.  Damages the fire-based enemies 1.5 times more, where as the ice-based enemies get only half the damage.
description.name: Cold Beam

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 30]\nAttacks surrounding monsters with a thunder bolt.  All monsters in the range receive damage.
description.name: Thunder Bolt
